{"tid":942162,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾看女團舞秒變「無感情鼓掌機器」　網民大讚：男偶像教材","createTime":"2018-12-15T12:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T02:37:09.000Z","uid":74065,"like":16,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb3725a94794a40ef7d02a9ace87c0e12ca89d0","tid":942162,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"王嘉爾看女團舞秒變「無感情鼓掌機器」　211萬網讚：男偶像教材<br />\n<br />\n2018年「MAMA」頒獎典禮壓軸場，14日在香港亞洲博覽館舉行，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中韓團GOT7成員王嘉爾（Jackson）是回到家鄉，在台上一喊廣東話就展現出主場氣勢。</span>不過他當晚觀看女團MOMOLAND演出時的反應也意外成為話題，被稱作是「男偶像標準教材」而登上熱搜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3765/d3765921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3765%2Fd3765921.jpg&h=c634356f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲<span style=\"color: red;\">GOT7王嘉爾被稱作「沒有感情的鼓掌機器」登上熱搜第一。</span>（圖／ETtoday）<br />\n<br />\n王嘉爾當晚觀看MOMOLAND演出時，面無表情、眼神放空的拍著手，這個畫面被微博網友截下後瘋傳，笑稱是「王嘉爾沒有感情的鼓掌機器」而登上熱搜。更由於許多女粉絲都不希望自己喜歡的偶像與異性有太多互動，因此王嘉爾的反應也被開玩笑稱作是「男偶像標準教材」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3765/d3765922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3765%2Fd3765922.jpg&h=48bb328c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾被捕捉「沒有感情的鼓掌機器」的畫面，正是女團MOMOLAND表演的時候。（圖／ETtoday）<br />\n<br />\n不過王嘉爾的反應並非是針對特定團體，當天畫面同時也捕捉到，他在GOT7被宣佈得獎時，第一秒仍是「沒有感情的鼓掌」，直到成員們起身後才發現是自己得獎了，立刻露出開心笑容，參與熱搜話題的211萬網友們也笑說：「他真的是太逗了！」<br />\n<br />\n嘎嘎冇令我失望<br />\n唔愛MOMOLAND<br />\n唔愛NANCY<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f08aac6758ad6420a2d4a8f4f6ca16cbccde3b","tid":942162,"uid":193951,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"希望各位男idol可以向嘎嘎好好學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc065e1a25b362ea824a5cd1efdc7aa7671844f","tid":942162,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f08aac6758ad6420a2d4a8f4f6ca16cbccde3b","tid":942162,"uid":193951,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"希望各位男idol可以向嘎嘎好好學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"希望粉絲都唔好條條仔射精"},{"pid":"aa71c7be46b400bc25578b05317751ece8d6b3b8","tid":942162,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"我愛MOMOLAND<br />\n我愛NANCY❤"},{"pid":"a73a5c1f7fcf03efe758cab9c520463dfa3c9b25","tid":942162,"uid":171594,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:52:48.000Z","msg":"Mml成班豬扒，梗係冇反應啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5770f4e613821e23a5c5968dbfadd78ade8b88","tid":942162,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"蝗嘉爾只係想solo <br />\n唔想比班垃圾member拖後腳阻住搵人仔姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93d003dc8248828cbd5fa81a43125efd82580aa","tid":942162,"uid":124114,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"蝗嘉爾原來港仔來?佢都幾勁WOR"},{"pid":"feed29645fe93171908dd059605d985cc6c9a789","tid":942162,"uid":89660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"我射精嘎嘎"},{"pid":"507b5a6204cc39dc9dc07de0f37831672a4a8df8","tid":942162,"uid":197813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e93d003dc8248828cbd5fa81a43125efd82580aa","tid":942162,"uid":124114,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"蝗嘉爾原來港仔來?佢都幾勁WOR"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:07:07.000Z","msg":"Old news is so exciting"},{"pid":"cd3949521a8a6e7aa4011f608c0ba9f04cc23891","tid":942162,"uid":30771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:13:32.000Z","msg":"wuli嘎嘎真的好棒"},{"pid":"3265d3bea81d